# Project logs/artifacts (ignore bulk logs, expose only final/best models)
# Covers all categorized subdirs: ppo_score_based/, ppo_event_based/,
# ppo_event_based_teammates/, alphazero/, archive_incomplete/, archived_logs/
project/logs/**
